  <summary date="2022-03-18T19:26:10Z" status="Introduced in House">Natural Immunity Transparency Act

This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to report within 30 days of the bill's enactment to Congress concerning natural immunity to COVID-19.

In particular, the report must compare certain outcomes for individuals who recovered from a COVID-19 infection without having received the vaccination and individuals who received the vaccination.</summary>
